Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想和你做朋友\NI want to be your friend again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  肖恩  怎么了\NW-why, Shaun? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,人们需要朋友\NPeople need friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这...\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,确实如此\NYeah, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但你说你希望我\NBut you said you wanted me -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别再打扰你  记得吗\Nto stop interfering, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要空间\NYou wanted space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你想  自己犯错\NYou wanted - to make your own mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,比起空间  我更需要朋友\NI need a friend more than I need space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是位优秀的导师  很好的朋友\NYou were a good mentor and a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  肖恩\NWell, thank you, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你无法想象这话对我有多重要\NYou don't know how much it means to me to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得\NBut I-I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可能要找个新导师\NI think you may need a new mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我活不久了\NI'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩十二到十八个月\N12 to 18 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.40,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你不要告诉其他人\NI'd appreciate it - if you didn't tell anyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我一人承受\NI-I will in my own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好  你做过全面病情检查吗\NOkay. Have you had a full work-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,当然做了\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是从其他地方\NIt could be a secondary tumor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,转移到你大脑的继发性肿瘤\Nmetastasized to your brain from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只发现了这个肿瘤\NIt's the only tumor found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是炎症或者感染症状\NIt could be an inflammatory or infectious process.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是肿瘤  肖恩\NIt was a tumor, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你该听听不同意见\NYou should get a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  我当了三十年的神经外科医生\NShaun, I've been a neurosurgeon for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这就是有力的「不同意见」\NI think that qualifies as a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你该问问其他人的意见\NYou should get a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,必须搞清楚是不是...\NYou have to know whether --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好  肖恩\NAll right, all right, all right, all right, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去问问其他人的\NI'll get a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我能去工作了吗\NCan I go to work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好  医生  诊断结果如何\NOkay, Doctor, what's your diagnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我醉了\NI'm drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你  是另一位医生\NNot you. Other doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于扭曲的程度\NUh, well, given the degree of the rotation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,以及骨折情况近乎复合伤\Nand the fact that the break is almost compound,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想目前的情况是双踝骨折\NI'd say we're dealing with a Bimalleolar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是三踝骨折\Nor Trimalleolar fracture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  还有呢\NVery good. What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色\NColor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,血流堵住了\NBlood flow is restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他的脚保不住了\NHis foot's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别啊\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在得给他复位  按住他的腿\NI'm gonna have to reset it now. Hold his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-不不不  -没事的\N- No.No, no, no. - No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就好\NIt's just gonna take a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你数到三\NI need you to count to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一\NOne...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一  二\NOne, two --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,卡登的腿没事吧\NIs Caden's leg gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他的腿这样有多久了\NHow long has his leg been like this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么\Nand how exactly did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到他时他就这样了\NWell, he's been like that since I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可能磕马路牙子上了\NHe probably tripped over a curb or something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是在路边找到他的\Nbecause that's where he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得有必要跟我讲两遍\NAny reason you felt the need to tell me twice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到他时的情形吗\Nthat you found him like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,朴医生  他得做手术\NDr. Park, boy's going to surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要一起来\NYou're going with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别走开了\NDon't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不该给我打麻醉吗\NShouldn't I be asleep for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你血液中的酒精含量会影响麻醉药\NYour blood alcohol level complicates anesthesia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你可能有脑震荡\Nand we think you have a concussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以得让你保持清醒\Nso we're gonna keep you responsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有给你做局部神经麻醉\NWe did give you a regional nerve block,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你应该没感觉\Nso you shouldn't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NCool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把液晶聚合板在近端倾斜两度\NBend the LCP plate over two degrees on the proximal end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,金冠成形钳\NContouring pliers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,血压下降  心跳加速\NBP is dropping, heart rate's rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,给他插管  立刻静脉注射肾上腺素\NLet's tube him. IV fluids and phenylephrine, stat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,得停止手术处理其他情况\NWe need to abort until we can get a handle on what else is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,做全身CT扫描  查血常规  做超声心动图\NGive me a full body CT, full blood panels, and an echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我和杰瑞德或许能更快找出问题\NI think Jared and I may be able to dig up an answer quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好  快去\NGreat. Get on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有想法了吗\NCome up with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有\NNeither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我在旧金山市立医院有个神经外科医生朋友\NI had a friend, a neurosurgeon, at SF Muni.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她看了扫描图\NShe looked at the scans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,得出相同的诊断  肖恩\NShe came to the same diagnosis, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我有不能动手术的胶质瘤\NI have an inoperable glioma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你该回去工作了  好吗\NI think you should go back to work, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去工作\NI need to go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,理智点\NBe reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\NBeg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,明智点\NBe reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\NI have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你会明白的\NOh, it'll be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,卡登到底怎么了\NWhat the hell happened to Caden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  他扭到脚踝了  我\NI -- I don't know. He twisted his ankle. I --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前在撒谎\NYou lied to me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还在撒谎  你个娇生惯养的孬种\NYou're lying to me now, you spoiled little coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,理智点\NBe reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他的朋友受伤了\NHis friend's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他很害怕  你把他吓坏了\NHe's scared, and you're freaking him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他生气了  但他说得没错\NHe's angry, but he's not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,卡登情况很糟  我们不知道原因\NCaden's in bad shape, and we don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得知道发生了什么\NWe need to know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  别担心他\NNo, no, don't -- don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说\NTalk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话\NYou tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有麻烦的  你只是在帮你的朋友\NYou won't get in trouble. You'll just...help a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们当时在宣誓入会\NWe were pledging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要想入会就得通过\NAnd there's -- there's this, uh, wheel of torture thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,「折磨之轮」的考验\Nyou got to do for initiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-折磨  -都是些脑残行为\N- Torture? - But it's mos-- - it's mostly stupid stuff, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,比如  喝一杯橄榄油\NIt's, like, like, drink a cup of olive oil
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,或者吃一勺肉桂粉\Nor eat a tablespoon of cinnamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,卡登转到了什么\NAnd what did Caden land on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,洗衣服\NLaundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他得洗衣服\NHe had to do laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  他得吃洗衣服用的东西\NNo, like, like, he had to, uh, eat th-those laundry things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,三十秒内看能吃多少\Nas many as he could in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,洗涤剂  吃洗涤剂\NDetergent? Eat detergent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他吃了多少\NAnd how many did he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  可能吃了六七...\NI don't know. Like six, maybe seven, seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他吃了洗涤剂\NHe ate detergent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会烧穿他的食道\NCould've burned a hole through his esophagus
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他的胃和肠子\Nor his stomach and intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请堵住那个出血点\NCatch that bleeder, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他别生孩子\NLet's hope he doesn't breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么  他难道不是个蠢蛋吗\NWhat? He isn't an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,消化道都修补好了\NWe have healthy bowel attached to healthy bowel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始缝合吧\NLet's close him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,梅伦德斯医生\NDr. Melendez?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,创伤科呼叫你去第二手术室\NThe trauma S.O.D. is asking for you in O.R. Number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有一台紧急开胸手术\NWe got an emergency thoracotomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能告诉我余下的缝合步骤\NWho can give me - the remaining steps for closing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,剪断锚定缝线  清理周边区域\NCut anchoring sutures, clear laps,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,将消化道归位\Nand reposition the bowel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,从十二指肠切除处移除夹钳\NRemove clamps from the duodenal resection site,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要遮挡下方动脉\Nkeeping clear of the underlying aorta,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,缝合筋膜  用环端0号单丝线\Nclose the fascia using a looped 0 monofilament,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,缝合真皮层以及表皮\Nclose the dermal layer, then reapproximate the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,并且需要确保筋膜缝合线\NAlso, you need to ensure no omentum is caught
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不穿过网膜\Nin the fascial suture line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,缝合吧\NClose him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,莫菲  你来做\NMurphy, you're lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,清理周围\NClearing laps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在你检查消化道的时候\NI will hold the repaired segment in place
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我来托着修补好的部分\Nwhile you run the bowel for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,消化道无异常  可以归位了\NBowel is clear - and ready to be repositioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩\NShaun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  你没事吧\NShaun, is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我丢了东西\NI lost something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在腹腔里吗\NIn the cavity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道它在哪儿\NBut I know where it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩\NShaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前把手术刀忘在这儿了\NI left my scalpel here earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该去做扩散张量成像\NYou should get Diffusion Tensor Imaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,DTI吗\NA DTI?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要准确诊断肿瘤的性质是很难的\NMasses are difficult to diagnose accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要拍更多片子\NYou should get more imaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,世人都会犯错\NPeople make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会去的  肖恩\NThat's not gonna happen, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手术刀不在这里\NMy scalpel isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这回又怎么了\NWhat happened this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他有内出血\NHe's got a bleed somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,去做胶囊内镜检查整个消化道\NI want a capsule endoscopy to check
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是否有出血点或者渗漏\Nthe entire length of the bowel for bleeding and leaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,做一份完整的凝血及代谢功能报告\NAnd get me a complete coagulation and metabolic profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\NOn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉斯曼医生要死了\NDr. Glassman is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么  他看上去没事啊\NWhat do you mean? He seemed fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他被诊断出有胶质瘤\NThey say he has a glioma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就是脑瘤\NThat's a brain tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他不去做DTI扫描进行确诊\NAnd he won't do a DTI scan to confirm the diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他有做二次诊断吗\NDid he get a second opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有的  但延误  未发现\NHe has, but delayed or missed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,或者误诊的机率\Nor incorrect diagnosis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,达到百分之十到二十\Nhas an occurrence rate of 10% to 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,医生也会犯错\NDoctors make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  我不知道你想要我做什么\NShaun, I don't know what you want me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我想请你先坐下\NI-I want you to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当人们想告诉你一些重要的事时\NThat's what people say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会这么说\Nwhen they want to tell you something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你说他要死了\NThe part about him dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不重要吗\Nthat wasn't the important part?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他不听我的建议\NHe won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他脾气很倔\NHe is stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-的确很倔  -很倔\N- That he is. - Stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他会听你的意见\NHe will listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识他时间更长\NOkay, you have known him longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是他的朋友  他信任你\Nyou're his friend, he trusts you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  我也不能逼他做任何事\NShaun, I can't make him do anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你  你是律师\NYou -- Y-You're an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅长撒谎或者操纵人\NI'm not skilled - at lying or manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想让我怎么办\NSo you want me to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我操纵他吗\NYou want me to manipulate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我利用他的关系及过去\NYou want me to use our relationship and our history -
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来迫使他去做这件事吗\Nto trick him into doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  求你了\NYes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不会就让他这么去死的\NI knew you wouldn't let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,患者出现弥散性血管内凝血\NOur patient has Disseminated Intravascular Coagulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有人能告诉我为什么这很糟糕吗\NCan anyone tell me why that is very bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,血管内出现弥散性凝血\NBlood clots form throughout the blood vessels
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,迅速消耗体内的凝血因子\Nand rapidly deplete the body's clotting factors,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,从而导致全身性出血\Nthereby causing a systematic bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们进退两难\NIt's also a catch-22.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们对付凝血\NIf we treat the clotting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能最终会出血至死\Nhe might end up with a terminal bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们治疗出血  他会因凝血而死\NAnd if we treat the bleeding, he'll have a terminal clot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们该怎么办\NSo how do we treat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要找出原因  进行根治\NWe figure out the cause. Treat the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还是清洁剂造成的伤害吗\NMore damage from the detergent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,边缘很清晰  不是的\NMargins were clear. It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他的脚踝处可能受到挤压伤\NHe could have a crush injury from his ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,或者在术中或术后发生细菌感染\NOr a bacterial infection he picked up before or during surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是因为服用药物\NIt might have been set off by drug use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是我们的问题\NOr we did this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我说「我们」  其实是指肖恩\NAnd by "We," I mean Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在手术室  他缝合的时候走神了\NHe spaced out in the O.R. when he was closing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就和现在差不多\Nkind of like he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-我在听着呢  -你在敷衍\N- I'm listening. - Comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有集中注意\NHe wasn't focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能当时夹伤了血管  这会造成...\NHe could've nicked a vessel, which could've caused --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说的可是肖恩\NOkay, we're talking about Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他确实不怎么说话  但他很专注\NYeah, he's quiet, but he was focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直都很专注\NHe's always focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他的针脚就像是缝纫机缝出来的\NHis stitches look like they came out of a sewing machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  并发症时有发生\NAll right. Complications happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接诊时他就状况很糟\NThe kid was in pretty bad shape when we got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,医师失误出现的可能性非常低\NPhysician error is way down on the list of likely causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,挤压伤最有可能\NCrush trauma being top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,先给他上新鲜冷冻血浆和晶体液\NGet him started on fresh frozen plasma and crystalloid fluids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在有空吗\NYou got a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个开放性问题\NWell, that's an open question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你找我有什么事\NWhat can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个患者出现弥散性血管内凝血\NI got a patient with DIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有一种可能是手术医师失误\NOne of the possible causes is surgeon error.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的患者  你的失误吗\NYour patient, your error?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是肖恩的\NShaun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他分心了  在手术中完全走神了\NHe got distracted - during surgery, spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他平时不这样\NIt's not like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他在手术室里从不错过任何细节\NOne place he never misses a beat is the O.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事吗\NIs there anything going on that I should know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他听到了一些坏消息\NHe got some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,关于什么的\NAbout what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是私人问题\NIt's a personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩因为私人问题而分心吗\NShaun was distracted by a personal issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么  莉亚回来了吗\NWhat, did Lea come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她有新男友了吗\NShe have a new boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他的电视被停了吗\NHis cable get cut off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我得了无法手术的脑胶质瘤\NI have an inoperable glioma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一年半可以活\N18 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,亚伦  我很遗憾\NAaron, I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\NMe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么我能做的吗\NIs there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望有\NI wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你早该告诉我的\NYou should've told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或者至少  你不应该告诉他\NOr at least you shouldn't have told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他的凝血因子依旧没有工作\NHis coagulation factors are still off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,挤压伤不是问题\NCrush trauma isn't the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他的毒理学检查是阴性\NAnd his tox screen came back clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-也不是因为嗑药  -我们并不能确定\N- It's not drugs, either. - We don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他输了太多血\NHe's had so many transfusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他血管里的血和他来时的血不一样了\Nthe blood in his veins isn't the same blood he came in with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,药物可能还在他的器官里造成...\NThe drugs could still be in his organs causing --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不想认为\NI get that you don't want to think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能是由你朋友造成的  但我们必须...\Nthat this could be caused by your friend, but we have to --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子是从兄弟会捉弄活动上来的  喝得烂醉\NThe kid came directly from a frat hazing, hammered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他没嗑药的几率有多大\NWhat are the odds he wasn't on drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该开始注射咪唑安定\NWe should start IV midazolam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,用碳酸氢钠中和...\Nand sodium bicarbonate to counteract --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是服用了安非他命的治疗方法\NThat's the treatment for amphetamines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的判断是错的\NIf you're wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会导致心律失常  危及生命\Nthat could cause a fatal arrhythmia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我会弄明白他嗑了什么药的\NI'll find out what drugs he's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你就准备通过问来弄明白吗\NYou're going to find out by asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱克之前对我挺坦诚\NBlake was honest with me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当你不是承认罪行的时候\NIt's a lot easier to be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,坦诚会容易得多\Nwhen you're not confessing to a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在这件事上我们没有太多选择\NWe don't have a lot of choice in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样的\NThat's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThanks for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\NYeah, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一眼看到你的时候就注意到你被划伤了\NNoticed it was cut when I first saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得应该处理一下\NFigured it should get cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我能抽点血吗\NIs it all right if I draw some blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想确保\NJust want to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有毒素和感染\Nyou don't have any toxins or infections.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\NSo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,护士说卡登有弥漫性血管内凝血\Nthe nurse said that Caden has DIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那是什么吗\NDo you know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,简单说就是他的身体\NWell, in short, his body is clotting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,同时在凝块和出血\Nand hemorrhaging at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们找不到原因\NIf we can't figure out what's causing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他就会死\Nhe'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,按住三秒\NJust hold that there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NAll done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱克  兄弟  你肯定嗑了什么\NBlake, buddy, you're on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的瞳孔扩张\NYour pupils are dilated,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在20℃的房间汗如雨下\Nand you're sweating in a 68-degree room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我可以把这个交给警察\NNow, I can hand this over to the cops
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你可以告诉我卡登到底嗑了什么\Nor you can tell the truth about what Caden's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,摇头丸\NMolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你直接问我的话我会和你说实话的\NI would've told you the truth if you'd asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你有时间谈谈吗\NYou have time to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩告诉你了\NShaun told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NHe did. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我更希望是你亲口告诉我\NI wish I would've heard it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NYeah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们是朋友  -我明白\N- We're friends. - I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-我想在你身边陪你  -怎么  你在生我的气\N- I want to be there for you. - What, are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该陪着你的\NI'm supposed to be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么  要干什么  握住我的手吗\NTo do what? To do what exactly? Hold my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  如果需要的话\NYes, if that's what's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我只想静静  好吗\NOkay, well, what I need is to be left alone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉了肖恩\NWell, you told Shaun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那可真明智\Nso that was a brilliant strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  好了  我明白\NOkay, okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢  蠢  蠢  蠢  好了吧\NStupid, stupid, stupid, stupid, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候当人们知道自己要死了时\NSometimes when people are told they are dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会做蠢事\Nthey do stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候他们身边的人会做蠢事\NSometimes people around them do stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩让你过来的\NShaun told you to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想劝我做更多影像  对吗\Nto try to convince me to get more imaging, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,亚伦  你不能放弃\NAaron, you can't stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-曼蒂不会让你放... -别\N- Maddie wouldn't have wanted you to stop -- - Don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别  别  你敢\Ndon't, don't, don't you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢\NDon't you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你要说什么\NWhat are you gonna say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,曼蒂是个斗士\NThat Maddie was a fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她从不放弃\NThat she never quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该去做个弥散张量成像\NAnd you should get the DTI.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不为你\NNot for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经接受了你的诊断\NYou've accepted your diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但肖恩没有\NShaun hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要接受\NHe needs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,尼尔\NHey, Neil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你的一个案子出现了并发症\NI heard there was a complication in one of your cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,卡登·赫里\NCaden Hauley?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是听说还是你在监控所有莫菲的案子\NHeard or have you been monitoring all of Murphy's cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我监控我部门的所有案子\NI monitor all my department's cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,弥漫性血管内凝血的18岁患者\N18-year-old with DIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,知道是什么导致的吗\NAny idea what set it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有并发症\NComplications happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他来的时候就状况很糟\NThe kid was in pretty bad shape when he got to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想知道你为什么同时做了两台手术\NI'm also wondering why you were in two surgeries at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你留下三个无人看管的新手住院医生\NYou left three first-years unattended?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们总是这么做的\NYou know we do this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不这样的话我们无法有效运转\NWe couldn't function efficiently if we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望卡登能渡过难关\NI hope Caden pulls through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么快就预约到了\NYou got a very quick appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我有后门  肖恩\NI have connections, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么听杰西卡的不听我的\NWhy did you listen to Jessica but not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,杰西卡也很聪明\NWell, Jessica's pretty smart, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但她和你说什么了\NYes, but what did she tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得现在不太适合谈这个\NI don't think this is a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候合适\NWhen is a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有很多要向你学习的地方\NI have a lot to learn from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要死了  就只剩下不到两年的时间学习了\Nand if you're dying, less than two years to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思让你们久等了\NSorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你的影像有点意外\NThere were some surprises on your images.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的诊断是不正确的\NThe previous diagnosis was incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的脑桥上有多形性成胶质细胞瘤\NYou have a Glioblastoma Multiforme located in your pons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不用我来告诉你\NI'm sure I don't need to tell you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是最具侵略性的脑癌\Nbut it's the most aggressive form of brain cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们估计还有约三到四个月的时间\NWe estimate three, maybe four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等你准备好了\NI can have my assistant get in touch with you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让我的助手联系你  给你介绍治疗师\Nto refer you to a therapist when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是有低血压  血液稀薄\NHe still has low blood pressure and thin blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说对摇头丸的治疗没有起效\Nwhich means the treatment for the MDMA didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以摇头丸不是问题所在\NSo the Molly wasn't the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定没有帮到他  但我们觉得他...\NIt certainly didn't help him, but now we think he --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的可能是卡登细菌感染了\NOur best guess is Caden has a bacterial infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,弥漫性血管内凝血\NDIC?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat happened there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还不确定\NUh, we're not sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他入院时就病得不轻\NHe was pretty sick when he came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候就是会出现并发症的\NI guess sometimes complications just happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,挺会讲话的\NInteresting choice of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,和梅伦德斯医生跟我说的居然如出一辙\NEerily similar - to what Dr. Melendez said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  他在讨论鉴别诊断的时候说过\NYeah, he said it during a differential.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概是记住了他用的词\NI guess the phrasing just stuck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,梅伦德斯不像那么放任你们的人\NIt's not like Melendez to be that laissez-faire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他一般会想知道每一个细节\NHe usually likes to know exactly why things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我敬佩他的地方之一\NOne of the traits I admire about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在想办法搞清楚\NYeah, well, we're trying to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但到目前为止  培养阴性\NBut so far, - the cultures are negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩的关腹操作是教科书式的\NShaun's closing was textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,也不像用了什么毒品\NDrug use doesn't seem to be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我没意识到是莫菲做的关腹\NI didn't realize Murphy did the closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他干得漂亮\NGood for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩\NShaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是的  有很多种不同的解释\NYes, yes, there are - many different explanations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我去听听其他意见  我去听了其他意见\NYou asked me to get a second opinion. I got a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我去做其他影像检查  我做了其他影像检查\NYou asked me to get more imaging. I got more imaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  你得接受\NShaun, you have to accept --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不接受\NNo, I don't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不接受  我是对的\NI don't accept. I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你错了  我要死了  肖恩\NNo, you were not right. I'm dying, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了  医生会犯错\NI said doctors make mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-对  他们是犯了错误  -他们犯了错误\N- Yeah, they made a mistake. - and they made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我剩下的时间比我们想得还少\NI have less time than we even thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩是对的  肖恩是对的\NShaun was right. Shaun was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,影像不可靠\NImaging is unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我去做的那个影像\NThe imaging that you asked me to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,影像检查会受到读片的影响\NImaging is subject to interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  研究表明专家依靠\NYes, studies have shown that experts rely on --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,依靠根据经验判断的\Non -- on subjective measures
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-主观的方法  而不是客观的  -够了\N- based on experience rather than object - No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-而不是客观的  -够了  够了\N- Rather than objective - No more, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,停  停  够了  够了\NNo. No, no. No more. No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-够了  -有很多一致的理论\N- No more. - Many theories consistent with --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以做活检来确认\NYou can do a biopsy to confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为肿瘤看上去都是一样的\Nbecause many tumors look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有些是可以治疗的\NSome are treatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-有些是可以治愈的  -求你停下来\N- Some are curable. - Stop, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有些是可以治愈的  是可以治愈的\NSome are curable. They're curable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,住口  求你了  住口  住口  别说了\NStop, please, will ya?! Stop, stop, stop talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-住口  -好\N- Stop! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住口\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有伤害你\NI am not hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  停\NOh, my God, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在帮你\NI'm helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是  你不是在帮我\NNo, you're not. You're not helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要理论\NI don't need theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要白板\NI don't need white boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要医生\NI don't need doctors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想去想那个肿瘤\NI don't want to think about the tumor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:22:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想去想我快死了\NI don't want to think about dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我要什么吗\NYou know what I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我其实想要什么吗  我想  我想\NYou know what I actually want? I want to -- I want to --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  开车去很远的地方\NI want to go - on a long drive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  我想吃煎饼\NI want to -- I want to eat pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看球\NI want to watch football.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在不是赛季  -天啊\N- It's not football season. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  不是赛季\NI know - it's not football season.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是想  想出去玩吗\NDo you mean you want to have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想出去玩\NI want to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你继续战斗吧\NSo you can keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是想  就继续战斗吧\NKeep fighting if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,无用  而且愚蠢\NIt's futile and it's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,或者  你也可以跟我一起\NOr you can come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他缺氧多久了\NHow long has he been hypoxic?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.19,0:24:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟前突然发作\NIt came on suddenly five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.71,0:24:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在用了100%高流量吸氧  数据也上不去\NHe's on 100% high-flow oxygen, and his numbers aren't budging.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他通气正常\NHe's ventilating fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定是肺动脉栓塞了\NHe must have thrombosed his pulmonary artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得在他心脏停跳之前溶栓\NWe need to dissolve this clot before his heart stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-杰瑞德  准备颈静脉通路  -好\N- Jared, prep for jugular access. - On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.97,0:24:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,50毫克tPA  现在注射\N50 milligrams tPA. Infusion now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.97,0:24:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,组织型纤溶酶原激活剂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.35,0:24:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快点  快点\NLet's go, let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好玩吗\NIs this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,情人节后的周六\NThe Saturday after Valentine's Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.05,0:24:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一年中她最喜欢的一天\Nher favorite day of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,比她生日还喜欢\Neven more than her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.41,0:24:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,商会把这地方装饰好\NThe Chamber of Commerce would decorate this place
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,准备一场没啥意思的自助餐  雇个DJ\Nand put out a crappy buffet meal, hire a deejay,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿上燕尾服\Nand I'd put on a tux,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.45,0:24:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿上黄色的小裙子\Nand she'd put on a yellow Belle dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.74,0:24:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她...\Nand she'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.06,0:25:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我戴好领结\Npin my bow tie on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.39,0:25:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮她戴上小小的胸花\Nand I'd pin a little yellow corsage on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.86,0:25:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们过来  吃饭  跳舞\NAnd we'd come and we'd eat and we'd -- and we'd dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.51,0:25:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,BGM: Your Smiling Face by James Taylor
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.51,0:25:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Whenever I see your smiling face ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.18,0:25:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ I have to smile myself ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Because I love you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.98,0:25:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Yes, I do ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.88,0:25:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你  亲爱的\NI love you, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.18,0:25:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我更爱你\NI love you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.92,0:25:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么想吗\NOh, you think so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.92,0:25:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你哦\NWell, I'll tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.43,0:25:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你爱我多少\NYou can take how much you love me,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.84,0:25:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦  我知道很多\Nwhich I know is quite a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.78,0:25:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你把你爱我的加倍  再加十\Nand then you can double it, and then you can add 10,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.69,0:25:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我有多爱你\Nand that's how much I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.49,0:25:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Tell me how much longer, if it grows stronger every day ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.42,0:25:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我更爱你\NI love you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.29,0:25:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Oh, how much longer? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.89,0:25:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ I thought I was in love a couple of times before ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ With the girl next door ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.03,0:26:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得当时想  「我知道这个瞬间\NAnd I remember thinking, "This is the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.80,0:26:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是我闭上眼睛\Nthat I know will be in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.65,0:26:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快要死去时  会想着的那个瞬间」\Nwhen I -- when I -- when I close my eyes to die."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.95,0:26:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我当时想  那时她肯定坐在我身边\NOnly I thought - that she'd be sitting there, right next to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.11,0:26:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会听到她再说一遍\Nand I'd hear her say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.12,0:26:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的玩具手术刀不见了\NI lost my toy scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.38,0:26:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫给我的那个\NThe one that Steve gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.00,0:26:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我觉得也是那把\NYeah, I figured that was the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.40,0:26:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我找了一整天\NI have been looking for a whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.11,0:26:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得可能它永远离我而去了\NI think it may be gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.14,0:26:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你死之后可能我还会来这里\NMaybe I'll come here when you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.54,0:27:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你对你女儿的记忆  足够了吗\NAre your memories - of your daughter enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.87,0:27:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不够\NNot even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.38,0:27:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要我再听你说一会儿\NDo you need me to listen to you anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.11,0:27:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  肖恩  你该回去了\NNo, Shaun, you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.48,0:27:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.58,0:27:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有培养结果没出来\NNot all the cultures are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.14,0:27:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但既然抗生素对他无效\NBut since he's not responding to any antibiotics,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.20,0:27:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以排除细菌感染了\Nwe can rule out bacterial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.26,0:27:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不会有完美的解释\NIt was never a great fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.90,0:27:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这最好是手术失误\NIt's a better fit than surgical error.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.56,0:27:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是细菌造成的而且对一切都有抗性\NWhat if it is bacterial but resistant to all --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.96,0:27:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那他得死了\NThen he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.67,0:27:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是阵发性睡眠性血红蛋白尿症呢\NWhat about Paroxysmal Nocturnal Hemoglobinuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,几率几乎微乎其微\NPnh? The incidence - is literally one in a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.35,0:27:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,莫菲弄错的几率能有多大\NWhat's the odds of Murphy screwing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.21,0:27:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我信莫菲\NI'd put them about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.07,0:27:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是阵发性睡眠性血红蛋白尿症\NNo, it's not PNH.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.62,0:27:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,卡登的流式细胞正常\NCaden had normal flow cytometry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.24,0:28:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,蛇毒会引发消耗性凝血病\NExotic snake venom can trigger consumptive coagulopathies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.64,0:28:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,先兆子痫也可以\NSo can pre-eclampsia,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.86,0:28:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但他没有怀孕也不是条迷人的蛇\Nbut he's not pregnant and he wasn't charming snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.97,0:28:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,莫菲有什么想法吗\NMurphy, any thoughts here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.79,0:28:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你两肋插刀的时候到了\NIt is kind of your ass on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.07,0:28:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道为什么卡登有播散性血管内凝血\NI know why Caden has DIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.32,0:28:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我挤压了两钳之间的动脉\NI squeezed the artery between two clamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.21,0:28:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我恐怕弄裂了主动脉壁\NI must have ruptured the aortic wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.49,0:28:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,从而造成了假性动脉瘤\Ncausing a pseudo-aneurysm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.57,0:28:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错\NIt was my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.25,0:28:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,同时\NAnd also...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.20,0:28:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要上洗手间\NI have to make a bowel movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.83,0:29:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他在撒谎\NHe's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.65,0:29:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他要吐了\NHe's gonna puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.55,0:29:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他要去找格拉斯曼\NHe's going to Glassman.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.09,0:29:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉梅伦德斯医生我需要去吸收剂\NI told Dr. Melendez I had to make a bowel movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.90,0:29:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他信了\NI think he believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.85,0:29:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为你自豪\NColor me proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.90,0:29:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我有答案了\NI have the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.78,0:29:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩我希望你在指你的病人\NShaun, I hope you're referring to your patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.34,0:29:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但鉴于你现在在这\Nbut due to the fact that you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.66,0:29:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,假装在厕所里\Npretending to be in the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.88,0:29:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-我有些怀疑  -这是你的答案\N- I kind of doubt that. - Yes, it's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.14,0:29:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经\NWe already --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.08,0:29:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经有我的答案了  肖恩\NWe already have my answer, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.05,0:29:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能对你进行活检\NWe can't do a biopsy on you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.99,0:29:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为会有动脉阻碍\Nbecause of the arteries in the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.11,0:29:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就像卡登腹部的动脉\Nlike the arteries in Caden's abdomen,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.53,0:29:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不能移动你脑部的动脉  因为\Nbut we can't move the arteries in your brain because --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.87,0:29:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要去旋转木马\NWhy did we go to the carousel?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.05,0:29:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你不开心\NBecause you were sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.21,0:29:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我有什么不想做的\NWhat didn't I want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.23,0:29:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道答案吗\NDo you not know the answers to these questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.59,0:29:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道答案  肖恩\NI do know the answers, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.99,0:29:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为你知道\NI don't think you know the answers to these questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.89,0:30:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你没懂我  我要死了\NYou're not hearing me. I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.28,0:30:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还有希望\NThere's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.39,0:30:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  看着我\NShaun, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.19,0:30:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\NLook at me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.50,0:30:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有希望了\NThere is no hope for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.58,0:30:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,希望\NI mean, hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.25,0:30:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,希望是什么\NWhat -- What -- What -- What is hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.26,0:30:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望四十九号能成功防守\NYou hope the 49ers find a defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.49,0:30:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望4路公交按时到站\NYou hope the number 4 bus comes on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.14,0:30:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不代表他们就会奇迹般知道怎么对战\NDoesn't mean they magically learn how to tackle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.29,0:30:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不代表公交司机就能突然加速\NDoesn't mean the bus driver suddenly drives faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.04,0:30:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,希望与我无关\NHope is irrelevant for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.61,0:30:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,希望令人痛苦\NHope is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.61,0:30:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望我在所剩的时日里\NI don't want to spend what's left of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.43,0:30:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,原地无谓打转\Nchasing my tail around in a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.32,0:30:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\NYou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.09,0:30:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.46,0:30:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.72,0:31:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肿瘤在你头骨的底部\NYour tumor is located at the base of your skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.54,0:31:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,开颅活检可以让我们了解情况\NAn open cranial biopsy would tell us what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.80,0:31:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但会有血管阻碍\NBut there are blood vessels in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.74,0:31:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,活检会导致动脉瘤或是出血\NThe biopsy would cause an aneurysm or a bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.26,0:31:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们从你的鼻筛状板进入\NBut if we go through your nasal cribriform plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.04,0:31:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以避开侧方的小脑幕\Nwe can cross the tentorium on the contralateral side
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.26,0:31:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,避开所有血管\Nand avoid all those blood vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.18,0:31:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以通过你的鼻腔进行活检\NWe can do a biopsy through your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.87,0:31:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不会死\NYou can't die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.48,0:32:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去吐了\NI have to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.27,0:32:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们要怎么做  上报吗\NSo how do we do this? Do we file a report?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.37,0:32:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,私下跟安德鲁斯交流下吗\NTalk to Andrews personally?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.60,0:32:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要上报肖恩吗\NYou want to report Shaun?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.11,0:32:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想  但我们必须如此\NI don't want to. I think we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.91,0:32:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你很想这样\NNo, you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.07,0:32:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们也必须这样  如果我们目标\NAnd we'd certainly have to if our sole agenda
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.54,0:32:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是弄走肖恩\Nwould be to take down Shaun
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.73,0:32:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让你少一个竞争对手\Nand to give you one less person to compete against.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.67,0:32:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我们还是得「必须」\NAnd certainly, we'd absolutely "Have to"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.42,0:32:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,掩盖一个可能的致命手术错误\Ncover up and bury a possible fatal medical error
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.57,0:32:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们的终极目的是保护一个朋友\Nif our sole agenda was to protect a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,医院规定肯定会站在那个婊子一侧\NProtocol would seem to favor the bitch over the friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.13,0:32:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.28,0:32:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚吐了\NI threw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.71,0:32:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要报告失误\NWe have a duty to report errors
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.16,0:32:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他们才不会再发生\Nso they won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.18,0:32:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才会拯救生命\NThe process saves lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.84,0:32:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到底在避免重复什么错误\NAnd exactly what errors are we trying to avoid a repeat of?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.70,0:32:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你担心下次还会有自闭的外科医生\NYou worried about the next time an autistic surgeon operates
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.09,0:32:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在发现自己的良师益友要死于脑癌后\Non a drugged-up frat kid after finding out his mentor
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.93,0:32:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再给一个嗑药的孩子做手术吗\Nis dying of brain cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.42,0:33:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,梅伦德斯医生告诉我们了  肖恩\NDr. Melendez told us, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.50,0:33:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很抱歉\NWe're really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.73,0:33:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.89,0:33:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.40,0:33:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他会没事的\NI think he's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.79,0:33:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,医院规定之所以存在\NThe protocol exists
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.85,0:33:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了让我们不会问这种问题\Nso that we don't ask questions like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.68,0:33:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,听上去不是个好主意\NThat seems like a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.47,0:33:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信你自己的评价\NYou trust your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.95,0:33:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信摩根的评价吗\NDo you trust Morgan's judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.42,0:33:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信这所医院里所有医生的评价吗\NDo you trust the judgment of all the doctors in this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.74,0:33:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以评价  他们也可以\NIf you can make judgment calls, so can they.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.83,0:33:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我们需要规定\NThat's why we need these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.37,0:33:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,医院规定对这所医院里所有人都可以\NNo, the protocol is fine for everyone in this building,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.47,0:33:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,除了肖恩\Nexcept for Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.78,0:33:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会训斥我们任何人但他们会解雇肖恩\NThey'd reprimand any one of us, but they will fire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.45,0:33:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.22,0:33:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上报吧\NWe report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.21,0:33:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做了调查\NWe get the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.24,0:33:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,确保这种事情不会再发生\Nmake sure nothing like this ever happens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.89,0:33:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们告诉他们是我做的\NBut we tell them I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.11,0:33:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也会解雇你\NThey'd fire you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.66,0:33:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是什么坏事\NIt's not a terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.41,0:33:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞德怎么都会出局的\NJared's out the door either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.75,0:33:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以重新用药物治疗吗\NCan we get back to the medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.73,0:33:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,卡登还活着\NCaden is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.13,0:33:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们可以保持他活着\NIf we can keep it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.37,0:33:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会有任何流言蜚语\Nthere won't be any review.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.97,0:33:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人会问问题\NWhich means no one will be asking questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.64,0:34:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人需要给出答案\Nand no one will have to give answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.09,0:34:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所有都会消失\NIt all goes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.32,0:34:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,卡登如果死了我们就说实话\NIf Caden dies, we tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.58,0:34:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起面对结果\Nand we face the consequences together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.90,0:34:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.47,0:34:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.65,0:34:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我找到了我的玩具手术刀\NI thought I'd found my toy scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.46,0:34:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你回到团队中来  莫菲\NWe need you to come back to the group, Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.88,0:34:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,给假动脉瘤的成像给我\NGet me imaging on that pseudo-aneurysm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.68,0:34:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.70,0:34:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你对莫菲医生的看法\NDo you still feel - the same way about Dr. Murphy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.69,0:34:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是跟他刚来的时候还是一样的\Nas when he got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.90,0:34:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉斯曼医生给了我们一定的担保\NDr. Glassman gave us certain...assurances.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.83,0:34:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果肖恩表现得不是非常出色\N"If Shaun proves - anything less than excellent,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.97,0:34:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他没有展示出我认为他能达到的水平\Nif Shaun doesn't live up to everything I know he can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.13,0:34:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他会立刻被辞退\Nhe will be immediately released,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:35:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而我也会辞去我作为\Nand I will resign my position
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.72,0:35:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,医院院长的职务\Nas president of the hospital."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.73,0:35:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而你也写下来了\NAnd you wrote it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.98,0:35:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我确保了这句话会在会议备忘中\NI made sure it was in the minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.32,0:35:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩超出了我的预期\NShaun has exceeded my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.72,0:35:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也超出了我的  然后呢\NMine, as well, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.62,0:35:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我对格拉斯曼医生的看法也没有变化\NAnd my feelings about Dr. Glassman have not changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.12,0:35:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.34,0:35:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要给他做手术\NWe need to cut him open.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.67,0:35:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一旦给他手术  他就会死\NWe cut him open and he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.19,0:35:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们看到动脉之前他就会大出血死亡\NHe'll bleed out before we can even get the artery exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.31,0:35:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不动手术  他会死\NIf we don't cut him open, he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.39,0:35:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别动他\NDon't cut him open.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.23,0:35:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,莫菲  如果我们不\NMurphy, if we don't --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.22,0:35:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该从他的大腿里装一条\NWe should insert an endovascular graft
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.67,0:35:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,血管内移植血管\Nthrough his leg instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.93,0:35:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,从内部解决问题\NFix it from the inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.10,0:35:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我在腹主动脉大扩张做过\NI've done that for large abdominal aorta dilations,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.28,0:35:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是一台漫长的假动脉瘤切除\Nbut this is a lengthy dissecting pseudo-aneurysm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.11,0:35:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会更安全\NIt's safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.23,0:35:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,动脉壁已经受影响了\NThe aortic wall is already compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.79,0:35:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会完全破裂\NCould rupture completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.13,0:35:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,凯登会在移植血管内的气囊放气的瞬间死亡\NCaden could die as soon as we deflate the balloon inside the graft.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.07,0:35:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但什么都不做会要了他的命\NBut doing nothing will kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.60,0:35:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也不尽然\NNot definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.81,0:36:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,凯登也有机会能够\NThere's still a chance Caden will simply come out of this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不用动手术也能活下来\Nwithout any surgical intervention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.80,0:36:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,5%  或者10%的几率\N5%, 10% maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.86,0:36:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是毫无机会\NNot nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.66,0:36:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是在知道肖恩闯祸之后\NAnd we're doubling down on Shaun
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.77,0:36:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还要踩上一脚\Nafter we know he caused this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.48,0:36:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这在发病和死亡病例研讨会上能有什么效果\NHow's that gonna look at an M&M?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.38,0:36:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信肖恩的想法\NI trust Shaun's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.20,0:36:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他会犯别人不会犯的错误\NHe makes mistakes no one else would make,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.19,0:36:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但他有我们从来没想过的救治方法\Nbut he also makes saves none of us would have ever thought of.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.49,0:36:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.77,0:36:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气\NYou're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.03,0:36:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是觉得你不应该在这里工作\NI still don't think you should be working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.99,0:36:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得代价还是太高\NI don't think the trade-off is worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.61,0:36:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我给他准备手术\NWell, let's prep him for surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.12,0:36:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抽出导线  雷兹尼克\NPull the guide wire, Reznick.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.27,0:36:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,推入移植血管\NI'm passing in the graft.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.50,0:36:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就在假动脉瘤的上方\NYou're right over the pseudo-aneurysm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.13,0:37:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,给气囊充气  释放移植血管\NInflating the balloon to deploy the graft.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.97,0:37:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,放气\NDeflating.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.96,0:37:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做吗\NCan I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.37,0:37:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太易损了\NIt's delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.86,0:37:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有\NNo, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.96,0:37:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要么成功要么失败\NAnd it will either work or it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.81,0:37:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我的想法错了\NIf my idea is wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.84,0:37:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他就会在我们完成下一步的时候立刻死亡\Nhe'll die as soon - as we complete this next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.56,0:37:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应该背负着这种责任\NYou shouldn't have to live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.09,0:37:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个手术室里发生的一切都是我的责任\NEverything that happens in this room is my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.80,0:37:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们一起来\NWe'll do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.84,0:38:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放气\NDeflating.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.04,0:38:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都不要回家\NNobody's going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.22,0:38:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我为这个团队以及我们今天所做的感到骄傲\NI am proud of this team and what we accomplished today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.75,0:38:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我请大家在哈利·霍普喝东西\NDrinks are on me at Harry Hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.54,0:38:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要庆祝吗\NWe're celebrating?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.45,0:38:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是场灾难  我们走运而已\NToday was a disaster, and we got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.33,0:38:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.06,0:38:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但你走运的时候  你就应该庆祝\NBut when you get lucky, you celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.41,0:38:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.09,0:39:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的职业生涯的某一刻\NAt some point in your career,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.82,0:39:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,病人会死在你手上的\Nyou're going to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.11,0:39:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望在事情发生的时候\NAnd I hope for your sake there's a doctor out there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.42,0:39:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,会有一名医生相信你\Nwho still believes in you when you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.57,0:39:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都在这里\NIt was there all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.28,0:39:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去喝酒了  但是我想让你知道\NI have to go drinking, but I wanted you to know --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.13,0:39:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是静脉注射的伤口吗\NIs that from an IV?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.15,0:39:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了活检\NYou did the biopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.33,0:39:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.06,0:39:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个小型的神经胶质瘤\NI have a low-grade glioma.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.52,0:39:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是脑干胶质瘤吗\NNot a GBM?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.34,0:39:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你了\NI told you --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.06,0:40:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,癌症  肖恩  还是癌症\NCancer, Shaun. It's still cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.80,0:40:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我得接受开颅手术\NI have to undergo brain surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.66,0:40:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不是我自己做  所以很可怕\Nwhich is really scary because I'm not the one performing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.50,0:40:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,每周五次  为期六周的放疗\NFive days a week - for six weeks of radiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.13,0:40:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有十周的化疗\N10 more weeks of chemotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.95,0:40:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\NAnd then?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.04,0:40:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后\NAnd then...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.85,0:40:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能有点运气\Nwith a little luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.10,0:40:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下一赛季就能去看超级碗了\Nyou and I can go to the Super Bowl next season.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.53,0:40:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会死的\NYou're going to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.25,0:40:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还有希望\NThere's hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.26,0:40:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧  去跟你的朋友们玩吧\NNow go. Go have some fun with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.80,0:40:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  首先我要告诉安德鲁斯我犯的错误\NYes. First I have to tell Dr. Andrews about the mistake I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.67,0:40:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  不可以\NShaun, y-you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.93,0:40:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,方案很清楚  报告能救命\NProtocol is clear, and reporting saves lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.79,0:41:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说凯登在恢复中\NAnd I hear Caden is on the road to recovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.42,0:41:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你的错误并不会太大\Nso your mistake couldn't have been too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.54,0:41:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我犯了错\NNo, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.94,0:41:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  我明白\NShaun, I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.50,0:41:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是安德鲁斯医生会利用这件事情\NBut Dr. Andrews will use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.59,0:41:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得格拉斯曼医生在你被雇佣时\NAnd do you remember the commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.02,0:41:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,做出的承诺吗\Nthat Dr. Glassman made when you were hired?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.25,0:41:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证你会很出色的对吧  肖恩\NI promised you'd be excellent, right, Shaun?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.72,0:41:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的表现很好\NAnd you have been excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.81,0:41:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能给安德鲁斯医生这个借口\NYou can't give Dr. Andrews this excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.81,0:41:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有很好\NI was not excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.63,0:41:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次  我表现不好\NThis time, I was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.78,0:41:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但外科医生每一次都要表现出众\NAnd surgeons have to be excellent every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.45,0:41:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧  肖恩\NRight, Shaun?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.21,0:41:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你同意他这么做吗\NYou agree with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.22,0:41:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让他为了保住我的工作而撒谎\NI'm not gonna ask him to lie to save my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.42,0:41:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么做\NDon't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.44,0:41:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是肖恩的决定\NIt's up to Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.44,0:41:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你的判断\NI trust your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.30,0:41:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么做不是要伤害你\NI'm not doing this to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.98,0:41:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.51,0:42:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友\NWe are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.52,0:42:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.93,0:42:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.02,0:42:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我也爱你\NI know. I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.12,0:42:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我更爱你\NI love you more.


